{"tid":1257791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"再一次證明香港人係好厲害","createTime":"2019-06-25T18:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T02:02:34.000Z","uid":50663,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56ac884ba1cec9ac7e0e5a6320f04bf93f787a70","tid":1257791,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:12:01.000Z","msg":"我衷心自豪身處於呢一代。<br />\n<br />\n無人可以諗過 其實可以用好多方法去抗爭<br />\n而且仲成功自發性 無大台 無領袖下 將所有諗法變成行動。用行動去宣傳比世界知 我地香港人呢一刻艱苦作戰中，但係我地永不言敗，不成功 不死心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢夢到大家用傳媒壓力 遊行 罷工 佔領 靜坐去抗爭呢一種傳統方法<br />\n<br />\n唔得？<br />\n<br />\nOk 唔緊要。<br />\n<br />\n我地有設計界代表：畫漫畫諷刺時弊 製作短片上youtube 將一段段扣人心弦既612片段製作小新聞 poster 傳單 文章等<br />\n<br />\n音樂界奇才：一首又一首既改歌、一眾虔誠基督徒 天主教徒 佛教徒用詩歌去激勵士氣。<br />\n<br />\n文宣外交部：有巴打諗到用眾籌去登報、聯署、用email要求限制有關人等出入境、甚至審查居留權、宣傳做選民等<br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得好多好多網站、專頁、小店用唔同方法去支持呢次運動。另外亦有唔同既專業人士發聲用最有力既證據去守護香港: 記者 議員 律師 醫生護士 救護員 消防 文職警察 廚房叔叔等等<br />\n<br />\n今日發起既派傳單道歉 更令我滿腔熱淚，我諗邊有地方示威之後條街仲乾淨過平時、不合作運動仲要咁有禮貌同你道歉？一班愛香港既人示範比你知，我地做得到。<br />\n<br />\n藉住呢段野 我想同所有努力過巴絲打 前線或文宣部 專業人士還是學生哥 首先講句多謝 多謝你地為自己同香港人出左一份力 出左一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我知道未成功，所以我地要繼續攜手努力，打埋下半場。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我非常幸運 出生在香港。"},{"pid":"37a9dfa58c8a0a95cab9197dd89c6e9a4f2f4f6b","tid":1257791,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"革命搖籃 are you ready?"},{"pid":"efcf2e58d3053ed0c639f2e062edb3e5a247729a","tid":1257791,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:13:08.000Z","msg":"一講下半場我諗起5:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de27db3d0372c813a8af8b8dd0862c5a04a4cec7","tid":1257791,"uid":160537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"香港人好撚團結同高質"},{"pid":"80e1987cba07196483c3379635c3cf5c87fb5be0","tid":1257791,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efcf2e58d3053ed0c639f2e062edb3e5a247729a","tid":1257791,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:13:08.000Z","msg":"一講下半場我諗起5:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"拿 我無諗過之前有贏 我係覺得呢場運動未完咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cf9c78b6a04e5183a7c0866d7b70d236dc931f","tid":1257791,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FinHGDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFinHGDx.png&h=357b537c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整咗幅圖，求share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw 冇暫緩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a>"},{"pid":"1f9d74cb34a36560232d65146f55b8b189eac5fb","tid":1257791,"uid":200274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:15:12.000Z","msg":"爸爸媽媽 我哋有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/PoNmjU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/PoNmjU</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好撚叻！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/daFFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/daFFcS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2fafaa5cd66b006aed2454570b676e24e68ec355","tid":1257791,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"唔記得講 文宣部既擾敵戰術 入藍絲page分化 高招"},{"pid":"d4db997ff5675e2111de0c1e762c0d92110cc40c","tid":1257791,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=